description:
Paying Half month broker's Fee

2bedroom and 1 bathroom apartment in South Boston. Hardwood floors, renovated bathroom. Walking distance to neighborhood restaurants. 
12' high ceilings Stainless Steel Appliances, Dishwasher, custom top-down bottom-up shades, NEST thermostat for high efficiency and energy savings.

Tenant responsible for cable and heat - electric. Owner pays trash, hot water and rest of building costs.
